source_text:
The [](item://occultism:iesnium_anvil) is a [#](AA00AA)Marid[#]() infusion.
This anvil has some improvements:
1. Is unbreakable;
2. Can exceed the maximum level of enchantments by 1;
3. Marid will pay half of the showed level cost (round up);
4. The cost increase of working with the same item is reduced;
5. The maximum cost limit is increased;

To set the destination, you''ll need a compass. Right-click to place it and shift+right-click to remove it.
+ A standard compass takes you to the world spawn;
+ A compass attached to a lodestone takes you to the top of it. (After placing it in the wormhole, the lodestone can be broken);

target_text:
目的地を設定するにはコンパスが必要です。右クリックで配置、shift+右クリックで削除。
+
+ ロッジストーンに取り付けられたコンパスは、その頂上に行く。(ワームホールに置いた後、ロッジストーンを壊すことができる);
+ "RTP "と名前を変えたコンパスはランダムテレポートとして機能する;

source_text:
+ A compass renamed "[#](AA00AA)HOME[#]()" teleport for your personal spawn point;
+ A compass renamed "[#](AA00AA)RTP[#]()" acts as a Random Teleport;
\
Alternatively, you can use special compasses:
+ [](item://minecraft:recovery_compass) teleports to the location of your last death, works only for players;
+ [](item://occultism:vitality_compass) teleports to the linked creature, it needs to be in a loaded chunk;
